322
00:14:35,019 --> 00:14:36,299
We didn't win, either.

323
00:14:36,340 --> 00:14:37,899
Weren't they all draws?

324
00:14:38,019 --> 00:14:39,539
A draw is better than losing.

325
00:14:39,539 --> 00:14:41,659
I didn't expect the seniors to be so skilled.

326
00:14:41,659 --> 00:14:43,139
They're all really amazing.

327
