342
00:15:12,340 --> 00:15:14,100
We don't have a participant for this event.

343
00:15:14,539 --> 00:15:15,259
No participant?

344
00:15:15,259 --> 00:15:16,059
Do we have anyone?

345
00:15:16,539 --> 00:15:17,340
Typing.

346
00:15:17,340 --> 00:15:18,259
Do we have anyone?

347
00:15:18,259 --> 00:15:19,100
