354
00:15:26,379 --> 00:15:27,860
You call that typing?

355
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:29,500
I just peck with one finger.

356
00:15:29,700 --> 00:15:31,460
My comrades call it the "woodpecker style."

357
00:15:31,779 --> 00:15:32,580
Then what do we do?

358
00:15:32,980 --> 00:15:33,620
Are we just...

359
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:35,000
