360
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:35,940
Don't do that.

361
00:15:35,940 --> 00:15:36,740
If there's no other way,

362
00:15:38,659 --> 00:15:39,779
I know how to type.

363
00:15:40,980 --> 00:15:41,779
How about...

364
00:15:41,899 --> 00:15:43,179
I give it a try?

365
00:15:43,460 --> 00:15:44,460
Try what?

366
00:15:44,460 --> 00:15:45,100
We have someone.

367
00:15:45,100 --> 00:15:45,620
He'll do it.

368
00:15:45,620 --> 00:15:46,379
We have someone.

369
00:15:46,679 --> 00:15:47,259
Please.

370
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:48,220
Ready...

371
00:15:50,379 --> 00:15:51,000
Go!

372
00:15:59,539 --> 00:16:00,340
