373
00:16:02,860 --> 00:16:03,659
Twenty seconds

374
00:16:05,340 --> 00:16:06,139
Fifteen seconds

375
00:16:07,500 --> 00:16:08,299
Ten seconds

376
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:09,899
Come on!

377
00:16:10,259 --> 00:16:10,720
Come on!

378
00:16:11,379 --> 00:16:11,980
Steady!

379
00:16:11,980 --> 00:16:12,700
Three

380
00:16:12,820 --> 00:16:13,620
Two

381
00:16:13,779 --> 00:16:14,580
One

382
00:16:14,580 --> 00:16:15,259
Stop

383
