405
00:17:04,859 --> 00:17:06,220
It's because...

406
00:17:06,319 --> 00:17:06,740
although

407
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:08,339
I did type more characters than her,

408
00:17:08,339 --> 00:17:09,099
however,

409
00:17:09,099 --> 00:17:11,980
