410
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:12,759
Three errors.

411
00:17:12,759 --> 00:17:14,640
Whereas she has no errors.

412
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:16,119
So the winner should be her.

413
00:17:16,559 --> 00:17:17,359
Alright.

414
00:17:20,359 --> 00:17:21,759
Then I declare

415
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:22,759
