417
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:26,019
the winner of Speed Typing is

418
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,359
Xie Yingzi.

419
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:37,200
We're in trouble, big trouble.

420
00:17:37,519 --> 00:17:39,500
Looks like we're going to lose.

421
00:17:39,779 --> 00:17:40,839
Who's to blame?

422
00:17:41,319 --> 00:17:42,339
It's all on you.

423
00:17:42,559 --> 00:17:43,359
You and Boss Li.

424
00:17:43,759 --> 00:17:45,680
A game of chess you clearly had in the bag,

425
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:47,339
