431
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:56,640
We lost because of him.

432
00:17:56,740 --> 00:17:57,799
Alright.

433
00:17:57,960 --> 00:17:59,640
Between us, we're

434
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:00,720
