435
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:02,640
Let's not fight among ourselves.

436
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:04,559
The most important thing now is to figure out

437
00:18:04,559 --> 00:18:06,400
how we can win this back.

438
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:07,359
Right.

439
00:18:07,519 --> 00:18:09,000
We have to count on Teacher Liu

440
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:10,119
