441
00:18:10,119 --> 00:18:11,680
With Teacher Liu, how could we lose?

442
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:13,039
That's right.

443
00:18:13,039 --> 00:18:14,039
Yeah. Come on!

444
00:18:14,319 --> 00:18:16,200
These grandpas and grandmas are amazing.

445
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:16,859
But,

446
00:18:16,859 --> 00:18:19,079
