453
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:34,799
If I asked him to be my mentor,

454
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:36,880
do you think he'd accept me?

455
00:18:37,079 --> 00:18:37,680
Alright.

456
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,519
Stop putting yourselves down.

457
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:41,259
Keke,

458
00:18:41,599 --> 00:18:43,259
how is your ukulele preparation going?

459
00:18:43,759 --> 00:18:46,039
I...

460
00:18:46,079 --> 00:18:46,880
Everyone,

461
00:18:47,079 --> 00:18:48,400
I think the break is just about over.

462
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:49,900
Shall we continue?

463
00:18:51,279 --> 00:18:51,960
Sure.

464
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:53,599
You... I mean...

465
00:18:53,599 --> 00:18:54,880
Teacher Liu, you just...

466
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:56,359
Uncles and Aunties,

467
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:57,480
let's

468
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:58,700
continue.

469
00:18:58,960 --> 00:19:00,180
Continue.

470
00:19:00,319 --> 00:19:01,000
Let's go. Let's go.

471
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:02,539
Let's go.

472
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:04,799
Teacher Liu, you go first.

473
00:19:04,799 --> 00:19:05,500
Teacher Liu goes first.

474
00:19:07,019 --> 00:19:07,640
Hurry up.

475
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:08,119
It's okay.

476
00:19:08,299 --> 00:19:08,599
It's okay.

477
00:19:10,059 --> 00:19:11,420
Next up is our

478
00:19:11,420 --> 00:19:12,920
final competition event:

479
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:14,400
the singing contest.

480
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:16,039
The first to perform

481
00:19:16,039 --> 00:19:18,559
is the singer from our Youth Team,

482
00:19:19,039 --> 00:19:21,400
Xia Keke.

483
00:19:21,400 --> 00:19:22,480
Keke!

484
00:19:22,839 --> 00:19:23,640
Go for it!

485
00:19:23,700 --> 00:19:25,799
Keke!

486
00:19:25,799 --> 00:19:26,400
Go for it!

487
00:19:26,819 --> 00:19:27,420
Good luck!

488
00:19:27,839 --> 00:19:29,720
