516
00:23:16,420 --> 00:23:17,660
It wasn't a waste.

517
00:23:17,940 --> 00:23:19,259
After today's competition,

518
00:23:19,259 --> 00:23:20,460
we truly feel that

519
00:23:20,460 --> 00:23:21,660
