531
00:23:36,779 --> 00:23:37,740
We have to admit,

532
00:23:37,740 --> 00:23:40,099
indeed, each new generation surpasses the last.

533
00:23:40,099 --> 00:23:41,539
Each generation is stronger than the next.

534
00:23:41,539 --> 00:23:42,460
No, no.

535
00:23:42,859 --> 00:23:43,819
Isn't that Gou'er Ye?

536
00:23:44,900 --> 00:23:45,619
Gou'er Ye!

537
00:23:46,460 --> 00:23:48,339
Why are you running away?
